{"tid":1136983,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Vodafone 指華為隱藏後門，華為官方回應：常見現象","createTime":"2019-05-03T11:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T19:52:38.000Z","uid":50534,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36b6faa6aa6b02a5fd8e945c65ccb917dee6c3ca","tid":1136983,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"華為自去年起面對外國的質疑，有關旗下產品的安全問題已經忙得不可開交，不過問題總是纏繞著他們。。。<br />\n<br />\n日前外國媒體彭博社報導指電訊營運商 Vodafone 表示發現華為於 2011 年所提供的軟件中有疑似後門的問題。內容指 Vodafone 發現華為為 Vodafone 的意大利業務提供的設備存在漏洞，而他們指分別在 2011年和2012年均發現安全性漏洞，不過很快被修復。<br />\n<br />\n而對於有關的報導，華為日前發出一份聲明，表示他們在設備中隱藏後門的說法絕對不真實。華為更表示彭博社的報導所指的是一種維修及診斷功能，而情況在整個行業都很常見，還有漏洞也是的常見現象，更指出該些漏洞早已在七年前得到糾正。<br />\n<br />\n不過之前被發現硬件有不應出現的零件，電話資料又被強制傳送到中國侍服器，現在又發現所謂的後門，而今次事件的解釋又帶點牽強 &ndash; 如果只是一種維修及診斷功能，為何被發現後要修復呢？不過怎樣也好，華為總算很快地回應有關問題。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/05/03/huawei-official-response-vodafone-back-door-allegations/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F05%2F03%2Fhuawei-official-response-vodafone-back-door-allegations%2F&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=5e3e7e18\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/05/03/huawei-official-response-vodafone-back-door-allegations/</a>"},{"pid":"b94e5e338249ed4940a46ac025f8e08f8c34c53b","tid":1136983,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:53:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;百步笑百步&rdquo;</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc42e1e4453ef750695c679f58685648b165251","tid":1136983,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T19:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔出奇啦"},{"pid":"f246ea29610ea60063e45521da07c6c8f97ed15e","tid":1136983,"uid":233530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T19:52:38.000Z","msg":"常你老母"}]}